{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":" 1. (The Prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم) frowned and turned away.","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:2","price":" 2. Because there came to him the blind man (i.e. ‘Abdullâh bin Umm-Maktûm, who came to the Prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم while he was preaching to one or some of the Quraish chiefs).","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:3","price":" 3. And how can you know that he might become pure (from sins)?","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:4","price":" 4. Or he might receive admonition, and the admonition might profit him?","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:5","price":" 5. As for him who thinks himself self-sufficient,","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:6","price":" 6. To him you attend;","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:7","price":" 7. What does it matter to you if he will not become pure (from disbelief: you are only a Messenger, your duty is to convey the Message of Allâh).","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:8","price":" 8. But as to him who came to you running,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:9","price":" 9. And is afraid (of Allâh and His punishment).","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:10","price":" 10. Of him you are neglectful and divert your attention to another,","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:11","price":" 11. Nay, (do not do like this); indeed it (this Qur’ân) is an admonition.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:12","price":" 12. So whoever wills, let him pay attention to it.","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:13","price":" 13. (It is) in Records held (greatly) in honour (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfûz),","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:14","price":" 14. Exalted (in dignity), purified,","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:15","price":" 15. In the hands of scribes (angels).","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:16","price":" 16. Honourable and obedient.","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:17","price":" 17. Be cursed (the disbelieving) man! How ungrateful he is!","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:18","price":" 18. From what thing did He create him?","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:19","price":" 19. From Nutfah (male and female semen drops) He created him and then set him in due proportion.","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:20","price":" 20. Then He makes the Path easy for him.","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:21","price":" 21. Then He causes him to die and puts him in his grave.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:22","price":" 22. Then when it is His Will, He will resurrect him (again).","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:23","price":" 23. Nay, but (man) has not done what He commanded him.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:24","price":" 24. Then let man look at his food:","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:25","price":" 25. We pour forth water in abundance.","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:26","price":" 26. And We split the earth in clefts.","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:27","price":" 27. And We cause therein the grain to grow,","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:28","price":" 28. And grapes and clover plants (i.e. green fodder for the cattle),","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:29","price":" 29. And olives and date-palms,","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:30","price":" 30. And gardens dense with many trees,","arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5788,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:31","price":" 31. And fruits and herbage","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5789,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:32","price":" 32. (To be) a provision and benefit for you and your cattle.","arabic":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5790,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:33","price":" 33. Then when there comes As-Sâkhkhah (the second blowing of the Trumpet on the Day of Resurrection)","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5791,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:34","price":" 34. That Day shall a man flee from his brother,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5792,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:35","price":" 35. And from his mother and his father,","arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5793,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:36","price":" 36. And from his wife and his children.","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5794,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:37","price":" 37. Everyman that Day will have enough to make him careless of others.","arabic":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5795,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:38","price":" 38. Some faces that Day will be bright (true believers of Islâmic Monotheism),","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5796,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:39","price":" 39. Laughing, rejoicing at good news (of Paradise).","arabic":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5797,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:40","price":" 40. And other faces, that Day, will be dust-stained.","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5798,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:41","price":" 41. Darkness will cover them.","arabic":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5799,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:42","price":" 42. Such will be the Kafarah (disbelievers in Allâh, in His Oneness, and in His Messenger Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم, etc.), the Fajarah (wicked evil doers).","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5800,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa","Chapter Abasa","Surah 80","Chapter 80","He Frowned","عبس"]}